Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:04.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello,\NI see you were able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:09.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:17.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Always by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:21.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,always you're so lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:27.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, an examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:46.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:50.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, come again,\NI'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. is it ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:01:00.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was the one that place a horse in the sand,\Nmaybe on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the miniature garden?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:06.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,An unsaddled horse without a rider,\Nwill escape if it's pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For now, let's be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:24.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The dizziness and nausea don't lessen,\N even though I have been properly taken my medication
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:31.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And sometimes my knees are trembling\Nnon stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., now, look, my knees are trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NLet's increase your medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And then, for a while,\Nplease look at the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, that would be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That would be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:57.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Miura-san?\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah! \N help me ... please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:09.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's Miura Makiko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the ballet prima donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:18.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa intended sexual harassment ...!\N{\3c&H585657&}That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After doing such an indecent thing,\Nare you trying to run away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Coward! Harassing Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura-san, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Professor, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's wrong! A misunderstanding! I did nothing ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:43.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}Ultimatum,\NI want the 7 million until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the money is..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:51.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mm you see,\Nyou can't buy without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she went..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:04.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll take that along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's 220 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, receiving exact amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:17.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\3c&H585657&}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Were you hungry?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:23.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's your name?\N{\3c&H585657&}Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:28.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan?\NI'm also waiting for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We're waiting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis too?？\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since mom will surely come,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,until then,\Nlet's eat this while waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:04.95,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.94,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:12.51,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.95,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:24.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:28.96,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:40.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:59.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, I really like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll give you this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis is not eating?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm fine because I have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is this, Dr. Miyagawa? \Nabout the sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything like sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah, you don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For this sort of occasion,\Nwith the proper permission of the patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been recording them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That would be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:44.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh? Miura-san?\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, at that moment\Nto touch the patient was a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A doctor that doesn't care\Nabout a patient that fell down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's not a doctor.\N{\3c&H585657&}No, the contact is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh?\NI think I saw that face somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is she something like a ballerina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The former prima donna, Miura Makiko-san\N{\3c&H585657&}former?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:08.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since her husband's dead, two years ago,\Nshe hasn't come out to front stage due to her depressive condition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if you told that to the media,\Nit's something serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It'd have been better just to do\Ndiagnosis through image only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In that way I would never been accused\Nwith this sexual harassment false accusation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414.4,37.8)}[T/N: he's doing a sort of pun here with his choice of words, that's kind of lost in translation]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that attitude that led to this kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,... What the hell? Hino\NI dare you to say that again..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. we have a problem, Miura-san's\Ndaughter is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why if you were watching,\Ndidn't you stop her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:35.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't know it was\NMiura-san's daughter..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My instructions weren't to damage\Nthe child, where's Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was taken away by being\Ndeceived by that woman, I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:46.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If something happens to that child,\Nit'll be your fault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Before that, let's look for her quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:53.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,While I was suffering of sexual harassment\Nby Prof. Miyagawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my daughter has disappeared!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:59.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that child is gone,\NI won't be able to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there's any chance of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll also die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:09.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you feel in some way uncomfortable?\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I were in her place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be too worry about the child,\Nto say those kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and immediately\NI'll go search for the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you please?\N{\3c&H585657&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's the commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can you stand? Do you wish\Nto rest a little over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please this way..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:38.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:43.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-kun, about the lady that was with\Nher daughter..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the geisha who had come to the Dr.'s room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I saw her leaving with the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:49.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:26.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis, your phone is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:33.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis, the clouds are really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you now together with a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis, we are now at the highest point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Hino!!\NPlease, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder where is mom now..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can I see her from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan, and your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dad has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't run down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sis, let's try to find mom\Ntogether, quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be alone anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you Miura Chika-chan?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan's mom is really worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:20.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where is mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She's waiting at the hospital. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:33.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Big sis, bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The training was fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's good\Nlet's do our best, next week too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aizawa Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:10.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to ride one more time?\Nif it's possible with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:13.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're almost a stranger..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:22.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:34.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:40.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yumeno?\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We're already preparing,\Nwe'll go to the parlor soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing! \Nquickly, come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'll return immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please hurry Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something has happened at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child it's my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,More important than life..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:17.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:24.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You worried me to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so happy you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who did you leave with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a big sis with candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:36.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I was lonely playing on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she was really friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't leave with people you don't know!\NI tell you that all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Either way, It's good that your daughter is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You said it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll take responsibility on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll led you to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Somehow,\Nthis may not end involving the police, but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who is this sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,patient? Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With this problem is enough!\N{\3c&H585657&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, mine is not a fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:34.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're going to mix the rice and\Nthe ingredients before cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \N{\3c&H585657&}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:51.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,egg too?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Next it's just to heat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's an unusual omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,this too is that person's recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:01.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about Yumeno-san's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:35.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe..,\NI think this is a dissociation case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:39.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san is the name of the geisha,\Nher real name is Aizawa Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:44.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think she probably suffers of\Ndissociative identity disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:50.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here is an Omurice that when you eat\Nmay have the same taste but..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If we see the entire Omurice as yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Each person, similar to this,\Nis made with various components.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:04.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there are times with good mood,\Nthere's also times with bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Usually in a person,\Nthey can be properly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:11.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,found in the same Omurice, in the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However,\Nwhen it's the case of dissociation state
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the person within oneself can have\Na number of states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:21.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One self is the red ketchup Rice\Nanother self, the yellow omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,both of them are the same cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but they don't feel\Nas the same omurice anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then,\Nwill they remember the same things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since this state of consciousness\N is not connected with this other
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,memory doesn't remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since the person doesn't remember\Nwhat was talking before
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he/she will be perceived as a terrible liar\Nby the surrounding people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The person would become more and more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When it comes to this terrible condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for each state of consciousness,\Nthe personality would change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It can become a child's personality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or sometimes an atrocious personality\Ncan appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean multiple personalities?\N{\3c&H585657&}In today's medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's called Dissociative identity disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey brother,\NI'm entering~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka-chan, good evening ~.\N{\3c&H585657&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yuriko-san, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:14.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's good, listen\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Bro\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you going out with a geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I heard it from the lady in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She says a geisha\Nwith white makeup and a traditional braid hairstyle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,constantly keeps coming here.\N{\3c&H585657&}It's not constantly..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just twice.\N{\3c&H585657&}Twice? I only knew about one..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well the first time,\Nshe came to return the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On the second time..well, Mizushima was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh what?\NYuriko-san, you met her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, Madoka,\Nwould you like an omurice too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You won't deceive me\Nwith an omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:45.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That geisha is Yumeno-san,\Na Rintaro's patient
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Patient?\N{\3c&H585657&}while it's still hot, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:51.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is she really a patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nakamura-san, good evening.\N{\3c&H585657&}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Konno-san, how are you?\N{\3c&H585657&}Fortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:11.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, a boring meeting\Ndoen't end easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hurry and look at Yumeno's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:22.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it? You wanted to talk.\N{\3c&H585657&}You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,again\Nthere's some favor I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:28.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just say it, I'll give you anything\Na bag?, a clock? a ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How nice, but even all of that would make me happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what I want the most now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's the roof for the geisha house\N{\3c&H585657&}eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:43.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since it's old, the leak in the roof is bad,\Nand mother is worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The 3 million that I passed you the other day\Nweren't enough to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:51.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The contractor called\Nto make an estimation said we need..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,just like this more, to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:58.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is said that most of the causes of \Ndissociative identity disorder occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,due to mistreatment and lack of affection\N during infancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:05.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that kind of painful experience during childhood\N is repeated many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to escape from the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the person would be pushed to another consciousness room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:13.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is thought to lead to dissociative disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By creating another personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the broken heart\Nbecomes detached from their own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:22.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san too,\Nsuffered of this disconnected heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,because of a painful personal experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Though I can't be sure unless I try to talk her\Nfor a longer period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And today also, that kind of situation happened with Prof. Miyagawa..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just don't summon her to the house again..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,since you are doctors and patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Brother, since you're not immune to women,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you should be really careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And Yuriko-san,\Nkeep watching him firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:49.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be told\Nthose things by my little sister, even now~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka, what are you doing\Nsince a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:57.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. this time,\Nthere is a wedding of my husband's relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:00.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so I thought of borrowing mom's kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuriko-san, this\Nis too plain, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.94,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.94,Remembering,,0,0,0,,there are a lot of things, you see,\NI'm giving this a lot of thought..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:25.00,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Wow! Your mom looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.45,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Did you wait?\N{\3c&H777779&}You're late
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.95,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder, if I could
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:03.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,have done something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}"You are not alone"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\u1}"and the door of the examination room is always open"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:31.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.,\NIt is better to eat something and not just the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't have any appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:42.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,this stabilizer., it's not at all effective
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,More, give me more, give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Dr.\N{\3c&H585657&}Oh? Is it..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I?\N{\3c&H585657&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:59.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It it safe to drink your medicine\Nwith that desperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:02.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone should stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay,\Nwhat dr. Yabe is passing to him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's just vitamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:16.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then, no matter how much he drinks,\Nit won't be effective~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:20.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yabe, who usually seems so cold,\Nshe's surprisingly gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:24.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Only towards Prof. Miyagawa, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why is there no effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something really bad just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:40.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura Makiko-san has informed\Nthat she's suing Prof. Miyagawa for sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:44.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, where is Prof. Miyagawa?\N{\3c&H585657&}He's become useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The elite is weak to punches like this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I call you.\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, will figure it out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand,\NI'll try talking to Prof. Miyagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, he also has his pride\Nbeing a professor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will he obediently receive an advice\Nfrom Hino-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be saying such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I'll have to entrust this \Nsexual harassment problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to a capable strong lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:10.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa-kun should hurry and get back on his own feet\Nand fight back, he's causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:11.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:16.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:30.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\3c&H585657&}Wha..what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:33.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I heard that stabilizers aren't effective.\N{\3c&H585657&}What? Did you come to call me a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:36.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That? This is ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Makiko Miura brought these to each examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to call my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:45.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really...\Nwhat is in this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My favorite comedian has this saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Comedian?\NThat doesn't suit the level of your education.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is the person I respect the most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is what he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:01.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Life is the one thing we go through in order to regret it."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:04.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In short, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:08.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you want to know the truth,\NI don't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:12.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah.. hurts..\N{\3c&H585657&}oh..hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:15.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Feels good?\N{\3c&H585657&}Didn't I say it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I got it, got it.\NIt feels good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:21.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't get it at all.\N{\3c&H585657&}Oh they are really effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:24.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And here you don't have to worry about your story being leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:28.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please talk with confidence Oh ....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Originally she ..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,came to the hospital to be treated for depressive symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:37.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah .. she was really talkative..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:41.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell what was real and what was a lie,\Nshe was merely bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:45.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My previous boyfriend was an Arabian millionaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I broke up with him because he was vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}vulgar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:53.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are people that think that the antonym\Nfor luxury is poverty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The antonym for luxury is vulgar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:01.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not just about how much money has the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:06.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ho~o It is indeed the word of a prima donna
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:07.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah! That was a full big time compliment
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:13.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. perhaps that's when she made a..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:17.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,positive transference with her doctor,\NI think that was the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:20.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that possible?\N{\3c&H585657&}In a therapy context, transference refers to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,redirection of a patient's feelings \Nand desires
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:25.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for a significant person in the past, \Nsuch as parents or lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:27.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to the therapist, unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.95,0:24:29.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.91,0:24:32.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, at that occasion I thought it was better to exaggerate\Nmy reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:35.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to please the patient..\N{\3c&H585657&}After that, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.47,0:24:38.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My medicine prescription worked well..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.51,0:24:41.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I thought she was  recovering steadily,\Nbut one day..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.93,0:24:45.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was this day, when I met,\Nthis person I really respect, Coco Chanel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.95,0:24:47.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In 1980, in Paris
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.92,0:24:49.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.93,0:24:54.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because Coco Chanel died in 1971, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.49,0:24:57.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are not supposed to lie, right?\NIn the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:24:59.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you weren't still born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.93,0:25:04.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see, that might not have been good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:08.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think she suffers from the histrionic personality disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:10.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why her disguise of lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.45,0:25:12.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you can't peel it off carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.53,0:25:17.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's think of this as her heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.45,0:25:19.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was feeling some strong stress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:23.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then she had to protect her heart,\Nif you say and do whatever to protect it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.92,0:25:27.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then you have to protect the lie.\N{\3c&H585657&}The lie protected her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. If we're talking of lychee, this is the peel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:35.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, uncovering her lie is the same as to peel the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.53,0:25:39.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was her bared heart\Nwhat she has been protecting in that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:42.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And that lie has been exposed by
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.44,0:25:44.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa who Makiko-san thought was a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.92,0:25:46.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With her bare heart wounded,\Nshe started
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.92,0:25:50.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to think of her doctor as the worst of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.41,0:25:54.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But at the same time she wants to become her friend,\Nso thinking in this way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:58.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she undergoes a sexual harassment commotion,\Nto go back once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:26:01.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\N{\3c&H585657&}Well, this time her conduct is mostly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.92,0:26:05.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that of someone that is considering to obtain\Naffection and interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.43,0:26:09.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurts! With a lot of understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.93,0:26:13.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with perseverance, make contact with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.45,0:26:15.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,without making fun of her lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.99,0:26:20.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please listen to the loneliness behind the lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.44,0:26:22.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't understand something like a loneliness behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:24.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Feel empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.43,0:26:31.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at feeling empathy\N{\3c&H585657&}Stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.42,0:26:34.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurts..!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.96,0:26:37.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Should go stronger?\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah Hurts, hurts hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.39,0:27:11.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:21.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.41,0:27:29.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew it, the director\Nof the Toshiminami gave it to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.43,0:27:31.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You have became close already?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.92,0:27:33.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.92,0:27:38.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, a souvenir,\Nyour favorite candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.43,0:27:43.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.41,0:27:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had a narrow escape from death~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.40,0:27:49.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are really a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:51.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:55.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ruriko, we should get going.\N{\3c&H585657&}Akira, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.44,0:27:57.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.91,0:28:20.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, is there's something wrong?\NIt's unusual for you to take a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.43,0:28:22.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And Yumeno-chan?\N{\3c&H585657&}She just went out a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.47,0:28:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but she'll return very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:25.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother,\NI'll start preparing for the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:27.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:31.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, what?, did you come to outing Yumeno\Ninstead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.41,0:28:33.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please enter.\N{\3c&H585657&}It's not that, not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.93,0:28:35.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since you're replacing the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:38.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought of introducing you an acquaintance contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.43,0:28:42.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've heard you had a terrible roof leak,\Nbut it doesn't look that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:45.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is that you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.42,0:28:49.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, for the cost of the replacement of the roof\NI handed in to Yumeno-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.41,0:28:52.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Construction cost? How much did you hand in?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.91,0:28:56.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Initially 3 million, but later\Nshe told me another 7 million were needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.43,0:29:00.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A total of 10 million!? \N Yumeno told you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:03.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah,\Nshe said mom was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.51,0:29:06.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the case?\N{\3c&H585657&}No..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.43,0:29:13.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's that so..\Nso it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.42,0:29:16.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:19.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once she's back I'll have a severe talk to her,\NI'll ask her to return the money at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:23.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has Yumeno-chan,\Na bad guy to support?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:28.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the case..but..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.42,0:29:32.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.90,0:29:34.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.91,0:29:43.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sis Yumeno
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.48,0:29:47.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sis Yumeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.52,0:29:52.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(414.4,44.2)}Nutcracker "pas de deux"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.41,0:30:40.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.92,0:30:43.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.41,0:30:49.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, even if I tried to feel empathy\Nno matter what, the empathy is not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.00,0:30:53.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because, the biggest victim here is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.92,0:30:56.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,being falsely accused of sexual harassment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.40,0:30:59.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I haven't even told my family yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.91,0:31:01.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you, Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.93,0:31:05.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is a directive request, solve it somehow.\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.91,0:31:07.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.92,0:31:10.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.52,0:31:14.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.90,0:31:35.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.46,0:31:38.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.40,0:31:42.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Makiko Miura-san's "Nutcracker",\Nat the forth place I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.90,0:31:45.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, despite being Sunday, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.91,0:31:53.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura Makiko-san was such a great ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.01,0:31:56.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura Makiko, former name Sugawara Makiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.43,0:31:58.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Her mother was also a ballerina\Nthat represented Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.40,0:32:00.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sugawara Etsuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.42,0:32:03.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since she was 3 years old\Nshe began with ballet under the strict guidance of her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:06.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In 1998 she won the All-Japan Dance Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.41,0:32:10.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In 2001 she was the first Japanese person to join the Les Halles Ballet company.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.43,0:32:14.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,5 years later, in 2006,\Nshe was promoted to the highest position of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.51,0:32:17.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The following year she married Takumi, her now late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.42,0:32:20.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After becoming a mother,\Neven though she has continued being inactive
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:24.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,as Miura Makiko\Nshe has obtain lots of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.41,0:32:27.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The dance with his husband Takumi-san,\N the "Dance of the Sugar Plum Fairy and the Prince",
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.93,0:32:30.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's certainly a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.41,0:32:32.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, what? Did you dance Ballet?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.97,0:32:36.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a child I was forced by my mother\Nto go to a ballet school.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.92,0:32:38.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:40.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It became fun while I was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:42.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I even entered the medical school\Nballet circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.93,0:32:44.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.91,0:32:49.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, then, Fukuhara-kun,\Nwhat is this pas de deux?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.92,0:32:55.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.02,0:33:03.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.40,0:33:13.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Recently,\Nwhat you heard about the Australian dollar?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.92,0:33:16.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't you learn your lesson with the FX?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.94,0:33:19.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just now, I'm recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.50,0:33:21.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even after being on the run,\Nfrom the blue face debt collectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.93,0:33:24.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your throat may have pass through,\NOh, that's a nice hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.92,0:33:28.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This time I'm after a large profit,\NI want to go even to Macau.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:30.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Macao, eh..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:33.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Being called by the superiors, the Okama from Macao
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.41,0:33:35.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Being called from the lowers..too\NThe Okama from Macao
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.93,0:33:39.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.00,0:33:42.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,someone known?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.89,0:33:58.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought you're a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.42,0:34:00.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,weren't you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.91,0:34:03.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who said that I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.43,0:34:07.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.00,0:34:10.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.89,0:34:17.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are again exploiting that girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.41,0:34:19.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not say bad things of my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.89,0:34:22.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From a guest,\Nshe deceived him with 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.90,0:34:26.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I don't think\Nsomeone with such a weak spirit could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:29.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She had that director stretching\Nunder her nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.95,0:34:31.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it was the money to finance her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.99,0:34:34.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew it, it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.39,0:34:38.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If so, what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.91,0:34:41.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the mother of that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.40,0:34:43.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with extort from my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.42,0:34:46.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child will be unhappy every time you appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.42,0:34:49.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're being irresponsible,\Nlet that child be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.89,0:34:52.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to meddle\Nwith other people's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.41,0:34:59.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who understands Akira the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.92,0:35:02.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That girl, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.92,0:35:06.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,if I'm gone, she'll be lonely, she's gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.91,0:35:13.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Afterall,\NMothers are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.48,0:35:17.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:20.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.92,0:35:23.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave, old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.42,0:35:39.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.41,0:35:46.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.91,0:35:49.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.91,0:35:59.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.40,0:36:10.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.46,0:36:16.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.89,0:36:20.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet with that big sis again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.41,0:36:22.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The big sis with candies?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.40,0:36:26.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.40,0:36:28.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.50,0:36:37.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.92,0:36:42.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's "The Nutcracker".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.40,0:36:45.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Does mom listen to this occasionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.91,0:36:48.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, this song..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.91,0:36:52.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Was the one your mom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.43,0:36:55.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,danced with your dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.45,0:36:59.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But,\Never since dad died,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.92,0:37:03.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mom,\Ndidn't want to dance it with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.91,0:37:06.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.41,0:37:09.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan dances?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.91,0:37:11.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I dance, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.92,0:37:14.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will you dance with this big brother? right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.49,0:37:19.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's only a little.\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.92,0:37:28.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.42,0:37:32.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.89,0:37:35.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, for doing something without your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.99,0:37:39.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.91,0:37:42.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We came in behalf of Prof. Miyagawa\Nfrom the Toshiminami University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.91,0:37:45.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm Hino Rintaro, a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.40,0:37:48.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Entering without permission,\Nwhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.40,0:37:51.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That matter was left in the hands of the lawyer,\Nplease leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:56.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Grand Pas de Deux for the Sugar Plum Fairy\Nand her Prince in Confiturembourg"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.48,0:38:00.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The pas de deux is a dance\Nwith dancing steps for two people, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.91,0:38:02.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.42,0:38:04.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura-san, you..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.90,0:38:08.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you been trying to dance\Nthe pas de deux by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.41,0:38:13.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.39,0:38:17.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, have a look at Chika-chan's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.48,0:38:21.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Children can't keep on living\Nwithout her mother's affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.40,0:38:24.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, could you give a closer look\Nto Chika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.42,0:39:16.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.91,0:39:21.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.95,0:39:34.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.92,0:39:59.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.40,0:40:01.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.40,0:40:06.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.42,0:40:08.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.39,0:40:11.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't dance anymore, please don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:15.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not that..\N{\3c&H585657&}I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.90,0:40:18.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.. It's not because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.90,0:40:23.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.91,0:40:27.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.43,0:40:31.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chika-chan\Ndidn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.45,0:40:35.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, people that have lost their loved ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.90,0:40:39.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there are times when a big gaping hole\N appears in their heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.91,0:40:43.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even if they are already adults,\Neven if she is a mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.41,0:40:45.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at those moments, they have to cry\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.90,0:40:49.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.42,0:40:54.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miura-san,\Nin trying to protect in some way their broken hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:59.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,people resort to lies, and fallacies,\Nto escape from tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.91,0:41:02.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That\Nmay not be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.40,0:41:08.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, even that,\Nit's a means of keep on living, that's what I think
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.94,0:41:14.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please stop\Ntrying to work so hard by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:18.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.91,0:41:21.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For Chika-chan's sake too
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.40,0:41:24.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why don't you start the treatment one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.90,0:41:30.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Allow me to be in charge of it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.92,0:41:43.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you practice by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.89,0:42:03.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.91,0:42:14.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.91,0:42:38.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.39,0:42:40.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke, I'm home
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.40,0:42:44.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rain is falling quite hard, you'll catch a cold,\Nlet's enter, come in .
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.90,0:42:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.40,0:42:48.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.99,0:42:57.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.\NDid you come from the examination room?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.41,0:43:02.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, since it's Sunday, nobody is there\N{\3c&H585657&}Sorry, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.38,0:43:06.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm placing here a change of clothes.\N{\3c&H585657&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.89,0:43:08.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.91,0:43:11.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Would you like a sandwich?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.93,0:43:14.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll make you one now,\Nplease, change your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.41,0:44:03.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom's smell
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.39,0:44:36.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,alright..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.92,0:44:49.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.41,0:44:50.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.94,0:44:54.51,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop!\N{\3c&H585657&}You'll get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.51,0:44:56.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.92,0:44:59.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, let's enter\N{\3c&H585657&}Thank you~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.40,0:45:20.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.91,0:45:22.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Enter, come in, come in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.92,0:45:25.93,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the intrusion\N{\3c&H777779&}Come in, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.93,0:45:27.90,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom, welcome back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.90,0:45:34.40,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had to take care\Nof a child, Yuri-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.40,0:45:36.42,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I told you, go over there, Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.42,0:45:40.41,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Akira? Sounds like a boy's name,\Ncoming in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.41,0:45:43.41,Remembering,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say that kind of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.41,0:45:46.47,Remembering,,0,0,0,,just come in..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.47,0:45:49.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,nay..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.92,0:45:55.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,don't, don't, hahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.92,0:46:00.45,Remembering,,0,0,0,,That child,\Nit would have been better if I didn't give birth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.45,0:46:02.50,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.50,0:46:06.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.42,0:46:09.91,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Hey, say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.91,0:46:12.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.42,0:46:17.95,Remembering,,0,0,0,,me too,\Nsee you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.95,0:46:21.40,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Akira,\Nyou have a lot of candies
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.40,0:46:23.92,Remembering,,0,0,0,,don't waste them,\Nand lick them slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.92,0:46:29.91,Remembering,,0,0,0,,you got a poor person's mentality,\Nwho did you take it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.91,0:46:32.41,Remembering,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.90,0:46:41.40,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom! When are you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.41,0:46:45.91,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I kept you waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.91,0:46:49.98,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom!\N{\3c&H777779&}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.98,0:46:52.41,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.41,0:47:55.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.41,0:47:57.91,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.91,0:48:05.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.41,0:48:16.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.41,0:48:31.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.91,0:48:45.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.39,0:48:50.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What did happen to you\Nduring your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.95,0:48:58.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.91,0:49:04.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:09.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.92,0:49:16.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.40,0:49:25.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't come out now.. Stop it!\N{\3c&H585657&}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.96,0:49:39.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.48,0:49:45.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.40,0:49:50.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm happy you're so fixedly staring at me..
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.41,0:49:53.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to know your real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:55.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.90,0:50:00.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.91,0:50:07.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.42,0:50:20.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're not doing anything, what a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.41,0:50:28.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.90,0:50:34.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are guarding the wounded Akira-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.39,0:50:37.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You always do this, to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.39,0:50:40.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your own wounded heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.93,0:50:44.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,..what a boring man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.90,0:50:50.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not come inside of me ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.42,0:50:52.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop messing with Akira!
